soviets retrain thousands of soldiers returning from east germany 
who could face unemployment back home 
it was also possible he said for west germany to help in 
supplying housing but not for a certain category of soviet 
residents west german officials are concerned about the domestic 
political fallout of building housing specifically for returning 
soviet troops 
