to help steer millions of dollars worth of hud funds to a project 
he partly owned manafort said his firm was also paid 326000 to 
help developers get hud backing for a project in new jersey 
watt said he met with pierce to help developers win 28 million 
worth of moderate rehabilitation program subsidies for a suburban 
baltimore project 
