<TEXT>
us sen john east committed suicide because 
government doctors failed to diagnose and treat him for a thyroid 
disorder attorneys for the north carolina republicans widow told 
a federal judge tuesday 
this is a case about a death that never should have 
occurred attorney james hourihan said in closing arguments in 
priscilla easts 35 million wrongful death lawsuit against the 
federal government 
east convinced that late diagnosis of his condition had 
permanently impaired his intellect killed himself in his garage on 
june 29 1986 with carbon monoxide from a running car he left a 
note blaming his doctors saying they ruined my health 
but federal attorneys said east 55 freely chose to end his 
life and had been pronounced cured of hypothyroidism for 11 months 
when he died in greenville nc 
this man was able to control himself was lucid in the last 
six months of his life said assistant us attorney ira oring 
