<TEXT>
bonnie bedelia has been around long enough to 
know the percentages there are more good actors than good parts 
and a lot more good parts for men than for women 
theres usually one decent female part per film she says and 
the numbers have often worked against her lovers and other 
strangers was a bad role in a good film prince of 
