boy struck out on both counts die hard and die hard 2 
were fun but those movies belong to bruce willis 
even a big part in a good film can come up short such as her 
acclaimed role as auto racer shirley muldowney in the 1983 film 
heart like a wheel compliment her on it and the response is 
terse yeah it would have been nice if someone saw it 
but for presumed innocent there are no frowns or 
