holders of more than 70 percent of the most senior notes indicate 
they support the plan 
the notes are considered a key group for this deal which must 
be approved by 95 percent of each class of bond plus twothirds of 
preferred shareholders 
we believe that we can successfully negotiate final documents 
and complete a restructuring and are now aiming for midaugust 
matthews said 
