because its become part of the rate case and because its in the 
public and i want some facts out there 
he said the parties first came to the attention of meco 
executives in 1985 an internal investigation was conducted by an 
outside agency 
they found no evidence of misconduct with respect to the 
purchasing arrangement or contract with vendors ferguson said 
as a result no action was taken 
