congressional leaders on wednesday afternoon would focus on the 
budget talks which have been progressing slowly despite the 
presidents reversal of his no new taxes pledge 
the agendas a very simple one lets get a solution to the 
deficit get a package to come out of the summit and move 
forward sununu said 
